NOTICE OF ASSESSMENT LIEN
OWNER OF RECORD:
Gabriela Melissa Lopez and Andres Emmanuel Rivera
SCANNED
LIEN HOLDER:
Wortham Oaks Homeowners Association, Inc.
AMOUNT OF LIEN:
$2,443.36 ($1,878.36 homeowner assessments and late fees; $565.00
attorney's fees and expenses)
PROPERTY ADDRESS:
5952 Akin Place, San Antonio, Texas 78261
LEGAL DESCRIPTION:
Lot 12, Block 20, County Block 4913A, Wortham Oaks Subdivision,
Unit 8 (Enclave), Bexar County, Texas
Notice is hereby given that the above-described Property is encumbered and subject to indebtedness owed
to the lien holder by the Owner in the amount set forth above for due but unpaid assessments, late fees, legal
expenses, and filing fees, and that pursuant to the Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for
Wortham Oaks, Units 1, 2, 3 and 4, A Planned Unit Development, Bexar County, Texas, executed on November 25,
2005, recorded in Volume 11876, Page 148, Official Public Records of Real Property of Bexar County, Texas, as
amended by the First Amendment to Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Wortham Oaks,
Units 1, 2,3, and 4, A Planned Unit Development, Bexar County, Texas, executed on January 27, 2006, recorded in
Volume 11912, Page 410, Official Public Records of Real Property of Bexar County, Texas, as further amended by
the Supplemental Declaration of Covenants, Conditions, and Restrictions for Wortham Oaks Subdivision, Unit-8,
Bexar County, Texas, executed on May 20, 2014, recorded in Volume 16692, Page 923, Official Public Records of
Real Property of Bexar County, Texas as amended, the lien holder has a Lien on the Property described above for
said sums.
Notice is further given that the amount of the Lien continues to increase pursuant to the terms of the
referenced Declaration.
